室专辑《Problems》于 2019 年发行。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-get-up-kids-announce-2025-uk-and-european-tour-to-celebrate-25-years-of-something-to-write-home-about-buy-tickets-3792750">The Get Up Kids 宣布 2025 年英国和欧洲巡演以庆祝“Something To Write Home About”成立 25 周年的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
